title: Osumo - Sea Point
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Raw, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service healthy food cafe with a few locations in Cape Town. Menu is mostly veg and has fresh juices plus smoothies, salads, wraps, and sandwiches. Sample dishes include red quinoa salad with beetroot and roast butternut & danish salad.
streetAddress: Regent St, Sea Point, Cape Town
